{"tid":57908,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[無伏]雙截龍4 30/1登陸PS4及Steam","createTime":"2016-12-28T11:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T12:08:16.000Z","uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b5d8ed827562815d5b27912c20d3ef6273efaf1","tid":57908,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:42:18.000Z","msg":"「雙截龍」是當年其中一隻最經典的遊戲，開創了「橫向闖關」遊戲種類。系列的最後一集「雙截龍 III」在 1990 年推出，想不到相隔 26 年竟然會有新一集出現！<br />\n雙截龍系列原本由 Technōs Japan 開發和推出，2015 年由另一間遊戲開發商 Arc System Works 購入。現在他們宣佈推出「雙截龍 IV」，剛好慶祝原作面世 30 週年。<br />\n雖然在這個充滿 3D 超細緻畫質的年代推出，但「雙截龍 IV」完全忠於原作。畫面繼續像素風格，而且玩法和設計都和當年一致。全因為找來原作的幾個重要開發者，包括導演、製作人、角色設定、音樂、程式員。<br />\n「雙截龍 IV」將於 1 月 30 日在 PS4 和 Steam 推出，有興趣可以去官網看看。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y0f8RV4Q8t4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy0f8RV4Q8t4&d=7iYbtcZZeJhd3jzdZBIOaRpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=f73eb267\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y0f8RV4Q8t4</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.arcsystemworks.jp/dd4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.arcsystemworks.jp%2Fdd4%2F&d=7iYbtcZZeJhd3jzdZBIOaRpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=8423ebb3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.arcsystemworks.jp/dd4/</a>"},{"pid":"bbb734319a367a1ac26fd9b4356d2460eb760f66","tid":57908,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:47:01.000Z","msg":"吓<br />\n<br />\n除左褲諗住J<br />\n<br />\n以為4係3D CG<br />\n<br />\n屌你原來玩懷舊8bit畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df961ac411cca39913ccf2adff636d3f616e4b89","tid":57908,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吓<br />\n<br />\n除左褲諗住J<br />\n<br />\n以為4係3D CG<br />\n<br />\n屌你原來玩懷舊8bit畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以為係改game"},{"pid":"1c9271b6448a8c78039fbdad3d23155941633afa","tid":57908,"uid":28